38:39.800 --> 38:41.240
Whoo! Whoo!
Whoo! Whoo! Whoo!

38:41.240 --> 38:42.200
Hey!

38:42.200 --> 38:44.120
Bueno! Bueno! Bueno!

38:59.320 --> 39:02.200
Didn't he say he'd call?

39:02.200 --> 39:04.120
Do you want me
to wait with you?

39:06.040 --> 39:07.960
Yes, please.

39:10.520 --> 39:12.520
Where the fuck
is the second shift?

39:12.520 --> 39:14.440
I got a phone call to make.

39:21.080 --> 39:23.000
I got to go
to the hospital.

39:25.400 --> 39:26.840
Are you cold?

39:26.840 --> 39:27.800
No.

39:27.800 --> 39:29.240
No?

39:29.240 --> 39:31.640
You're all right?

39:31.640 --> 39:34.040
Don't wait too long, will you?

39:47.800 --> 39:49.720
Oh, shit.

40:00.520 --> 40:02.920
Pim, got to make
a phone call.

40:02.920 --> 40:04.360
Get out of here.

40:36.200 --> 40:38.120
Hello?

40:38.120 --> 40:40.520
Oh, is Bess there?

40:40.520 --> 40:42.440
One moment.

40:42.440 --> 40:44.840
Bess. Bess.

40:54.040 --> 40:55.480
Is that you, Bess?

40:55.480 --> 40:56.440
Hi.

40:56.840 --> 40:59.720
Oh, I'm sorry I couldn't
get to the phone earlier.

40:59.720 --> 41:01.640
That's ok.

41:03.400 --> 41:05.800
Don't you love me anymore?

41:05.800 --> 41:09.880
Oh...
Of course I do.

41:10.040 --> 41:11.560
Say so, then.

41:11.560 --> 41:16.840
I'd made up
my mind not to.

41:16.840 --> 41:19.720
Everyone says that
I love you too much…

41:19.720 --> 41:22.120
…and if you found out…

41:22.120 --> 41:24.520
…how much I loved you,...

41:24.520 --> 41:26.920
...you might get upset…

41:26.920 --> 41:30.280
...because we're not
together right now.

41:30.280 --> 41:32.200
Oh, Bess, never stop
saying you love me.

41:32.680 --> 41:33.640
You hear?

41:33.640 --> 41:35.080
Yes.

41:35.080 --> 41:36.520
No matter what anybody says.

41:38.440 --> 41:39.880
Yes.

41:42.760 --> 41:44.680
Say it, then.

41:48.520 --> 41:50.920
I love you so much.

41:55.720 --> 41:57.160
I love you, too.

42:06.280 --> 42:08.680
I can hear you breathing.

42:12.040 --> 42:14.440
Can you hear me?

42:49.320 --> 42:51.240
What are you thinking?

42:53.160 --> 42:56.040
That you're here.

42:56.520 --> 42:58.920
And what are you doing?

42:58.920 --> 43:05.160
Um... I'm touching your arms…

43:05.160 --> 43:08.520
…and your chest…

43:08.520 --> 43:12.360
…and your tummy

43:12.360 --> 43:16.200
and...

43:17.640 --> 43:20.040
...your prick.

43:22.440 --> 43:23.880
You're so huge.

43:23.880 --> 43:26.760
Ha ha ha!

43:26.760 --> 43:32.520
Jan will be home in
ten days for a week.

43:32.520 --> 43:33.960
Pardon?

43:34.440 --> 43:38.280
Jan will be home in
ten days for a week.

43:40.200 --> 43:41.160
Pits.

43:41.160 --> 43:42.120
Hi.

43:42.120 --> 43:44.520
What are you doing here?

43:44.520 --> 43:46.920
Where's Jan?

43:46.920 --> 43:50.280
I'm the only one back.
Hurt my wrist.

43:50.280 --> 43:51.720
They sent me home.

43:51.720 --> 43:52.680
Oh.

43:52.680 --> 43:55.080
He sends his love.

43:57.000 --> 43:58.440
How long have
you got off now?

43:58.440 --> 43:59.880
Only three days.

44:00.000 --> 44:01.240
Oh.

44:01.320 --> 44:03.240
Yeah. You know me.

44:05.160 --> 44:06.040
I'm back.

44:06.040 --> 44:07.960
Oh, sorry.

44:16.600 --> 44:19.000
How long
has she been asleep?

44:19.000 --> 44:20.920
What's the matter with you?

44:20.920 --> 44:22.840
Cat got your tongue?

44:25.720 --> 44:28.120
Have you taken my calendar?

44:28.120 --> 44:30.040
Huh?

44:30.040 --> 44:31.960
Have you taken my calendar?

44:31.960 --> 44:33.400
No, I have not.

44:33.400 --> 44:35.320
What would I want
with your calendar?

44:35.320 --> 44:37.240
Don't be ridiculous.

44:37.240 --> 44:38.680
You've taken it.

44:38.680 --> 44:40.120
I have not taken it.

44:40.600 --> 44:42.040
Yes, you have.

44:42.040 --> 44:43.480
I don't know what
you're talking about.

44:43.480 --> 44:45.400
What calendar?

44:49.720 --> 44:51.640
Where is it?

45:03.880 --> 45:06.280
Bess, you've got to
stop all this, you know.

45:06.280 --> 45:08.680
You've got to go on living
when he isn't here.

45:09.160 --> 45:10.600
I mean, he's not dead.
You're not dead.

45:11.080 --> 45:12.520
You know what I mean?

45:12.520 --> 45:16.360
You've got to stop it.

45:38.920 --> 45:40.840
Shh. It's all right.
It's nothing.

45:41.320 --> 45:42.760
What's going on?

45:42.760 --> 45:44.200
Go back to sleep.
It's all right.

45:44.200 --> 45:45.640
Was that Bess?

45:45.640 --> 45:47.560
No. It's ok.
It's all right.

45:47.560 --> 45:48.600
Bit of hysterics.

45:48.600 --> 45:50.040
No, no. It's all right.
I'll sort it out.

45:50.040 --> 45:51.480
We're not to have this
carry on in the house.

45:51.480 --> 45:53.400
I know. Just stay where you are.
Go back to sleep.

45:53.400 --> 45:54.840
It's terrible.

46:10.600 --> 46:15.880
Bess McNeill, for many years,
you've prayed for love.

46:15.880 --> 46:18.280
Shall I take it away
from you again?

46:18.280 --> 46:20.200
Is that what you want?

46:21.640 --> 46:25.480
Oh, no.

46:25.480 --> 46:27.400
I'm still grateful for love.

46:30.280 --> 46:32.680
What do you want, then?

46:37.480 --> 46:41.320
I pray for Jan to come home.

46:43.720 --> 46:46.600
He will be coming
home in ten days.

46:46.600 --> 46:49.480
You must learn to endure.
You know that.

46:54.280 --> 46:56.680
Oh, I can't wait.

47:01.960 --> 47:04.360
This is unlike you, Bess.

47:04.360 --> 47:08.680
Out there, there are people
who need Jan and his work.

47:08.680 --> 47:10.600
What about them?

47:14.440 --> 47:19.720
They don't matter.
Nothing else matters.

47:19.720 --> 47:23.560
I just want Jan home again.

47:24.040 --> 47:26.440
I pray to you.

47:26.440 --> 47:30.280
Oh, please,
won't you send him home?

47:34.600 --> 47:38.440
